DROP TABLE [stage].[Arrets];

SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO

CREATE TABLE [stage].[Arrests]
( 
	[id] [bigint]  IDENTITY(1,1) NOT NULL,
	[CB_NO] BIGINT,
	[CASE_NUMBER] [nvarchar](50),
	[ARREST_DATE] [datetime],
	[RACE] [varchar](50),
	[CHARGES_STATUTE] [nvarchar](255),
	[CHARGES_DESCRIPTION] [nvarchar](4000),
	[CHARGES_TYPE] [nvarchar](255),
	[CHARGES_CLASS] [nvarchar](255)
)
WITH
(
	DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN,
	CLUSTERED COLUMNSTORE INDEX
)
GO
